1
00:01:08,180 --> 00:01:09,992
[Episode 21: Penniless Means Helpless]

2
00:01:11,480 --> 00:01:12,920
Forget it.

3
00:01:12,920 --> 00:01:14,360
Let it be.

4
00:01:14,360 --> 00:01:16,909
My vacation will be over tomorrow anyway.

5
00:01:18,520 --> 00:01:21,407
Tomorrow, we won't...

6
00:01:23,880 --> 00:01:26,320
What about my meals?

7
00:01:26,320 --> 00:01:28,738
Time to cook for yourself, honey.

8
00:01:29,440 --> 00:01:30,685
Eat up.

9
00:01:39,079 --> 00:01:40,288
Xi Zhou has grown up.

10
00:01:40,288 --> 00:01:42,840
Why don't you ask her to support you?

11
00:01:42,840 --> 00:01:44,320
Yes, she has.

12
00:01:44,320 --> 00:01:46,131
She should have her own life.

13
00:01:46,840 --> 00:01:48,439
I try not to trouble her.

14
00:01:48,439 --> 00:01:50,297
It's a big deal after all.

15
00:01:52,079 --> 00:01:53,231
He comes.

16
00:01:58,248 --> 00:01:59,360
Hey,

17
00:01:59,360 --> 00:02:01,200
Wang Qiu Ping.

18
00:02:01,200 --> 00:02:03,480
It's been a long time since we met.

19
00:02:03,480 --> 00:02:05,320
You're prettier.

20
00:02:05,320 --> 00:02:07,330
- Your husband--
- Her husband died

21
00:02:07,330 --> 00:02:09,760
in a car accident after the divorce.

22
00:02:11,840 --> 00:02:13,760
Alright, hurry up.

23
00:02:13,760 --> 00:02:16,269
Let's see how much it takes to get a divorce.

24
00:02:18,479 --> 00:02:21,265
A car accident... after the divorce?

25
00:03:21,852 --> 00:03:23,260
[Ren Xi Zhou]
[QQ: 634321218]

26
00:03:25,400 --> 00:03:27,096
[You've earned a Qzone Cottage badge for mutual visits
with Ren Xi Zhou for 7 consecutive days.]

27
00:03:27,096 --> 00:03:29,228
[Keep it up for 30 days
to earn a Qzone Villa badge.]

28
00:03:37,009 --> 00:03:38,610
[Access permission required]

29
00:03:43,160 --> 00:03:45,253
What am I doing?

30
00:03:59,440 --> 00:04:03,080
You're all dressed up... at home?

31
00:04:03,080 --> 00:04:04,332
Come in.

32
00:04:20,759 --> 00:04:22,120
Do you have a straw?

33
00:04:22,120 --> 00:04:25,280
I heard that drinking without a straw

34
00:04:25,280 --> 00:04:27,072
would deepen nasolabial folds.

35
00:04:35,760 --> 00:04:37,600
I saw the casting call for <i>First Love</i>.

36
00:04:37,600 --> 00:04:39,760
I want to record an audition video.

37
00:04:39,760 --> 00:04:42,439
But I lack a narrator.

38
00:04:42,439 --> 00:04:43,530
Okay.

39
00:04:46,920 --> 00:04:48,163
I'm ready.

40
00:04:57,240 --> 00:04:59,160
Hello. I'm Zhu Qiao Fei.

41
00:04:59,160 --> 00:05:02,040
I played Jun Lan, the supporting male lead
in <i>Wish Fulfilled Early</i>.

42
00:05:02,040 --> 00:05:03,800
This is my pet, Bento.

43
00:05:03,800 --> 00:05:06,079
It mimics the environment.

44
00:05:06,079 --> 00:05:10,840
Likewise, I adapt my performance to each role.

45
00:05:10,840 --> 00:05:11,880
I want to play

46
00:05:11,880 --> 00:05:14,160
the supporting male lead in <i>First Love</i>.

47
00:05:14,160 --> 00:05:15,720
Your advice is appreciated.

48
00:05:15,720 --> 00:05:17,280
My performance will begin.

49
00:05:19,839 --> 00:05:21,951
We... welcome.

50
00:05:29,752 --> 00:05:31,879
Welcome...

51
00:05:31,879 --> 00:05:33,880
Mom. Li Nan Xi is too shy

52
00:05:33,880 --> 00:05:35,520
- to attract customers.
- Hey!

53
00:05:35,520 --> 00:05:38,028
After all, I did her a favor.

54
00:05:39,519 --> 00:05:40,839
Welcome.

55
00:05:40,839 --> 00:05:41,839
Welcoming me?

56
00:05:41,839 --> 00:05:43,026
- Yes.
- Okay.

57
00:05:43,800 --> 00:05:46,000
Mr. Li wants the property.

58
00:05:46,000 --> 00:05:47,480
As for

59
00:05:47,480 --> 00:05:49,959
the shabby tables and seats, they're unwanted.

60
00:05:49,959 --> 00:05:51,319
- Just remove them! Remove them.
- Okay.

61
00:05:51,319 --> 00:05:52,319
What are you doing?

62
00:05:52,319 --> 00:05:53,439
I'm calling the police.

63
00:05:53,439 --> 00:05:55,320
Yes, call the police.

64
00:05:55,320 --> 00:05:57,000
Call the police?

65
00:05:57,000 --> 00:05:58,280
Funny.

66
00:05:58,280 --> 00:05:59,360
This is my house.

67
00:05:59,360 --> 00:06:01,289
I can remove as I wish.

68
00:06:02,200 --> 00:06:04,000
- Do it.
- Come.

69
00:06:04,000 --> 00:06:06,200
- What are you doing?
- What? What?

70
00:06:06,200 --> 00:06:07,439
This is not your house.

71
00:06:07,439 --> 00:06:08,600
Get out of here!

72
00:06:08,600 --> 00:06:09,839
Ren Hong Xia,

73
00:06:09,839 --> 00:06:11,680
do you know any law?

74
00:06:11,680 --> 00:06:13,720
We haven't divorced.

75
00:06:13,720 --> 00:06:17,199
We're a couple,
and this is joint property. Understand?

76
00:06:17,199 --> 00:06:18,600
Even so, joint property

77
00:06:18,600 --> 00:06:20,399
shall be settled by both parties.

78
00:06:20,399 --> 00:06:22,360
It's illegal for you to remove unilaterally.

79
00:06:22,360 --> 00:06:23,810
You brat!

80
00:06:27,568 --> 00:06:30,040
Hello, Mr. Li. You're here.

81
00:06:30,040 --> 00:06:31,240
[Hongxia Diner]
Look.

82
00:06:31,240 --> 00:06:34,240
This is the property I mortgaged.

83
00:06:34,240 --> 00:06:35,807
What do you think?

84
00:06:40,000 --> 00:06:41,451
Nan Xi?

85
00:06:42,185 --> 00:06:43,560
Dad...

86
00:06:43,560 --> 00:06:44,771
Come here.

87
00:06:45,759 --> 00:06:47,350
Dad, I...

88
00:06:48,640 --> 00:06:50,098
Three,

89
00:06:51,440 --> 00:06:52,633
two,

90
00:06:53,839 --> 00:06:54,852
one.

91
00:07:09,519 --> 00:07:10,943
Xi Zhou.

92
00:07:44,200 --> 00:07:45,535
Is it good?

93
00:07:46,839 --> 00:07:48,360
Compared to the first time I saw you,

94
00:07:48,360 --> 00:07:49,480
you've improved a lot.

95
00:07:49,480 --> 00:07:51,199
So you recognized me?

96
00:07:51,199 --> 00:07:52,400
Why...

97
00:07:52,400 --> 00:07:55,040
Your line delivery was terrible then.

98
00:07:55,040 --> 00:07:56,720
You cared too much about your look,

99
00:07:56,720 --> 00:07:58,319
thus you

100
00:07:58,319 --> 00:08:01,360
kept one pose for the camera

101
00:08:01,360 --> 00:08:02,850
and wore a hat.

102
00:08:02,850 --> 00:08:04,639
A hat makes my face look smaller.

103
00:08:04,639 --> 00:08:06,640
I was a bit anxious about my look then.

104
00:08:06,640 --> 00:08:08,319
But I'm much better now.

105
00:08:08,319 --> 00:08:10,399
Thanks. If you need anything,

106
00:08:10,399 --> 00:08:11,763
just let me know.

107
00:08:14,160 --> 00:08:15,400
Can you show me

108
00:08:15,400 --> 00:08:17,336
your Qzone?

109
00:08:17,336 --> 00:08:18,512
What?

110
00:08:35,400 --> 00:08:37,264
What's going on between you and Ren Xi Zhou?

111
00:08:42,490 --> 00:08:43,742
Oh, right.

112
00:08:44,399 --> 00:08:45,840
My actor friend

113
00:08:45,840 --> 00:08:47,559
wants your advice.

114
00:08:47,559 --> 00:08:49,399
A role interests him,

115
00:08:49,399 --> 00:08:51,480
but pays poorly,
with a quick-tempered director,

116
00:08:51,480 --> 00:08:52,840
and a demanding producer.

117
00:08:52,840 --> 00:08:54,720
He really wants to play it

118
00:08:54,720 --> 00:08:56,240
and thinks it's good.

119
00:08:56,240 --> 00:08:57,600
So,

120
00:08:57,600 --> 00:08:58,935
should he go for it?

121
00:08:59,968 --> 00:09:02,086
Don't hesitate over what you like.

122
00:09:04,080 --> 00:09:05,360
You're right.

123
00:09:05,360 --> 00:09:07,919
Don't dawdle and miss the chance.

124
00:09:07,919 --> 00:09:08,960
Bye.

125
00:09:08,960 --> 00:09:11,150
If she posts anything, I'll let you know.

126
00:09:11,720 --> 00:09:12,909
I'm on your side.

127
00:09:32,760 --> 00:09:34,040
Close the curtains.

128
00:09:34,040 --> 00:09:35,320
Don't get tanned.

129
00:09:35,320 --> 00:09:37,120
You won't be tanned.

130
00:09:37,120 --> 00:09:38,480
You agreed to return.

131
00:09:38,480 --> 00:09:39,799
Why the tantrum?

132
00:09:39,799 --> 00:09:41,440
You said if I returned,

133
00:09:41,440 --> 00:09:43,928
you'd postpone the acquisition.

134
00:09:43,928 --> 00:09:46,557
Oh. Didn't I do that?

135
00:09:48,520 --> 00:09:50,320
If it's profitable,

136
00:09:50,320 --> 00:09:52,155
you wouldn't give up easily.

137
00:09:52,759 --> 00:09:54,395
You knew I was back in Nanwan,

138
00:09:54,395 --> 00:09:55,879
thus acquired her diner deliberately,

139
00:09:55,879 --> 00:09:57,960
and forced me to return, didn't you?

140
00:09:58,600 --> 00:09:59,955
So what if I did?

141
00:10:00,640 --> 00:10:03,382
You know why
I didn't stop you from going to Nanwan?

142
00:10:05,602 --> 00:10:06,720
Turn off the AC.

143
00:10:06,720 --> 00:10:07,826
Yes, Mr. Li.

144
00:10:23,280 --> 00:10:25,296
Turn on the AC.

145
00:10:31,560 --> 00:10:33,303
- Turn it on.
- Yes, Mr. Li.

146
00:10:37,120 --> 00:10:39,120
Because I want to teach you

147
00:10:39,120 --> 00:10:40,960
that one can give up pride,

148
00:10:40,960 --> 00:10:42,200
dignity,

149
00:10:42,200 --> 00:10:43,480
principles,

150
00:10:43,480 --> 00:10:45,640
but not money.

151
00:10:45,640 --> 00:10:47,919
Penniless means helpless.

152
00:10:49,720 --> 00:10:51,520
You're much thinner.

153
00:10:52,559 --> 00:10:54,948
You must have suffered a lot.

154
00:10:57,118 --> 00:10:58,640
Suffering can be good.

155
00:10:58,640 --> 00:10:59,919
It teaches you a lesson.

156
00:10:59,919 --> 00:11:01,994
Such a hypocrite.

157
00:11:03,039 --> 00:11:04,440
You're good,

158
00:11:04,440 --> 00:11:06,200
boasting about your art dream

159
00:11:06,200 --> 00:11:08,522
to your friends.

160
00:11:10,560 --> 00:11:13,307
A spoiled artist?

161
00:11:14,490 --> 00:11:15,879
Don't worry.

162
00:11:15,879 --> 00:11:17,840
Even if I know,

163
00:11:17,840 --> 00:11:19,680
I won't expose you.

164
00:11:19,680 --> 00:11:21,660
After all, you're my daughter.

165
00:11:21,660 --> 00:11:23,046
Nan Xi,

166
00:11:23,720 --> 00:11:26,280
I've been good enough to you.

167
00:11:26,280 --> 00:11:27,480
To get an investment,

168
00:11:27,480 --> 00:11:29,680
you exploit my marriage!

169
00:11:29,680 --> 00:11:31,840
I'm not forcing you to get married.

170
00:11:31,840 --> 00:11:34,240
I'm just introducing you to him.

171
00:11:34,240 --> 00:11:36,639
If you like him, stay and get married.

172
00:11:36,639 --> 00:11:37,800
If you don't,

173
00:11:37,800 --> 00:11:40,539
you can be a waitress or an artist.

174
00:11:42,600 --> 00:11:43,789
Really?

175
00:11:46,080 --> 00:11:47,299
Really.

176
00:12:23,643 --> 00:12:24,680
Please.

177
00:12:24,680 --> 00:12:26,280
Hello, Ms. Li.

178
00:12:26,280 --> 00:12:27,960
Sorry to keep you waiting.

179
00:12:27,960 --> 00:12:29,322
I'm Lu Shang.

180
00:12:30,880 --> 00:12:32,070
Have a seat.

181
00:12:36,960 --> 00:12:39,779
It's alright. I only waited for half an hour.

182
00:12:40,919 --> 00:12:42,160
It's 26 min.

183
00:12:42,160 --> 00:12:43,164
What?

184
00:12:43,799 --> 00:12:45,279
I'm helping my mom with her business.

185
00:12:45,279 --> 00:12:47,240
So I'm sensitive to numbers.

186
00:12:47,240 --> 00:12:48,387
Don't mind.

187
00:12:49,872 --> 00:12:51,597
Waiter, serve the food.

188
00:12:58,120 --> 00:13:00,200
Chef-made appetizer,

189
00:13:00,200 --> 00:13:02,336
pan-fried wagyu beef with pea puree.

190
00:13:03,480 --> 00:13:05,997
I have six. What about you?

191
00:13:06,592 --> 00:13:08,200
Let's eat first.

192
00:13:08,200 --> 00:13:09,557
Wait, wait!

193
00:13:23,052 --> 00:13:24,120
She has nine.

194
00:13:24,120 --> 00:13:26,320
I'm sorry, sir. I'll get you a new one.

195
00:13:26,320 --> 00:13:27,848
You're known for the best dishes

196
00:13:27,848 --> 00:13:29,279
and excellent service.

197
00:13:29,279 --> 00:13:30,879
How could you make such a basic mistake?

198
00:13:30,879 --> 00:13:32,919
I'll get you a new one,
and the charge is waived.

199
00:13:32,919 --> 00:13:34,416
Will this do, sir?

200
00:13:36,600 --> 00:13:37,737
Yes.

201
00:13:46,440 --> 00:13:47,463
Eat up.

202
00:13:49,000 --> 00:13:51,301
It's okay. Let's wait.

203
00:14:03,159 --> 00:14:04,200
Try it on

204
00:14:04,200 --> 00:14:06,240
to see if it fits.

205
00:14:06,240 --> 00:14:07,919
If you don't want to get married,

206
00:14:07,919 --> 00:14:09,519
tell me earlier.

207
00:14:10,440 --> 00:14:12,218
In case you regret.
